 based on transaction prices, there might be an (reward or reason for doing something) for buyers 
 to report low transaction prices at the registration of the title. 
 However, transaction prices were often public knowledge, and 
 many buyers wanted transaction prices to be known in order to 
 attract more sellers. 
 
 in this study using a survey of farmers) of land and 
 water used in crop production. The (money-related) analysis 
 is performed to decide/figure out individual (rewards or reasons for doing something) to 
 participate in water markets. In contrast, the money-based analysis provides the net return to (community of people/all good people in the world) 
 from market moves (from one place to another). In an money-based analysis, 
 move (from one place to another) payments are left out/kept out and prices are (changed to make better/changed to fit new conditions) for money-based values (explained in more detail 
 later in this paper). The following paragraphs explain 
 this procedure and the ideas (you think are true) used. 
